title: Windows 8 Core Upgrade x86 (Build 6.2.9200)
description:
Ripped from legit Windows 8 install disks. This is build 6.2.9200, NOT 8.1, NOT pro or enterprise. If you want pro, create and use an ei.cfg file.

System Requirements:

- 1 GHz processor with PAE/NX/SSE2 support
- 1 GB of RAM
- 16 GB available hard disk space
- 1024 x 768 or higher screen resolution in order to run apps
- Windows XP SP3, Windows Vista SP1, or Windows 7 for upgrade

*** Use KMPRF-CDFTG-GD8T7-N3K66-BPWXQ to install, then Microsoft Toolkit to activate.

*** If you successfully created and used an ei.cfg file to convert it to Windows 8 Pro, use Q6RKB-RXMKJ-T8NYW-P4FDP-J4YRQ to upgrade it to Windows 8 Pro with Media Center.
